                <title>In which our hero fails to heed his own rules</title>
                <link>http://grahambinns.com/blog/2013/08/01/in-which-our-hero-fails-to-heed-his-own-rules/</link>
                <comments>http://grahambinns.com/blog/2013/08/01/in-which-our-hero-fails-to-heed-his-own-rules/#comments</comments>
